[The cause or causes of the gastrointestinal illnesses in the American rowers is not clear. The posting implies that the source was the body of water where the rowing was done, but alternative sources such as food may be at work. - Mod.LL

More information from knowledgeable sources would be appreciated. - Mod.MPP

